oon**\\n  - Return to Karur, visit **Kalyana Pasupatheeswarar Temple** again for the evening aarti (free).  \\n  - Optional: Quick shopping for silk sarees at **Karur Silk Centre** (budget\u202f\u2248\u202f\u20b92,000\u2013\u20b93,000 if desired).\\n- **Dinner**\\n  - Treat yourself to a seafood platter at **Madhur Restaurant** (\u2248\u202f\u20b9350).  \\n  - Night\u2011cap: fresh coconut water from a street vendor (\u2248\u202f\u20b930).\\n\\n- **Departure**\\n  - Catch the 10:00\u202fpm express train back to your origin (same fare as Day\u202f1).\\n\\n---\\n\\n### Recommended Hotels (one per category)\\n\\n| Category | Hotel (approx. nightly rate) | Key Features |\\n|---|---|---|\\n| **Budget** | **Hotel Sree Krishna** \u2013 \u20b91,800 | Clean rooms, free Wi\u2011Fi, central location, includes breakfast |\\n| **Mid\u2011range** | **Hotel Gokul** \u2013 \u20b94,200 | Air\u2011conditioned rooms, rooftop restaurant, 24\u202fhr front desk |\\n| **Luxury** | **The Grand Karur** \u2013 \u20b99,500 | Deluxe suites, spa, in\u2011house dining, valet parking |\\n\\n*All rates are for a double occupancy room; taxes may add ~10\u202f%.*\\n\\n---\\n\\n### Approximate Cost Summary (per person)\\n\\n| Item | Budget (\u20b9) | Mid\u2011range (\u20b9) | Luxury (\u20b9) |\\n|---|---|---|---|\\n| Train (round\u2011trip) | 1,200 | 1,200 | 1,200 |\\n| Hotel (2 nights) | 3,600 | 8,400 | 19,000 |\\n| Meals (6 meals + snacks) | 1,200 | 1,800 | 2,500 |\\n| Local transport (auto/rickshaw, day car) | 1,200 | 1,200 | 1,200 |\\n| Entry fees / activities | 300 | 300 | 300 |\\n| Misc. (souvenirs, tips) | 1,000 | 1,500 | 2,000 |\\n| **Total Approx.** | **\u20b98,500** | **\u20b914,400** | **\u20b926,200** |\\n\\nEven the luxury scenario stays well under the \u20b950,000 ceiling, leaving ample room for extra shopping or an upgraded dining experience.\\n\\n---\\n\\n**Quick Tips**\\n- Book train tickets 2\u20133 days in advance to secure AC seats.  \\n- Carry small change for temple donations and street vendors.  \\n- Dress modestly for temple visits (shoulders and knees covered).  \\n- Keep a copy of your hotel\u2019s address in Tamil script for easy navigation.\\n\\nEnjoy a relaxed, culturally rich getaway in Mayanoor!  \\n\\nAPPROVE\",\"type\":\"TextMessage\"}}", "sender": "Travel_Planner_418d5148-8e86-4a47-b42b-bcc77017160e/418d5148-8e86-4a47-b42b-bcc77017160e", "receiver": "output_topic_418d5148-8e86-4a47-b42b-bcc77017160e/418d5148-8e86-4a47-b42b-bcc77017160e", "kind": "MessageKind.PUBLISH", "delivery_stage": "DeliveryStage.SEND", "type": "Message"}
